hn Madden, are subject to license to Electronic Arts Inc., and may not be otherwise used in whole or in part without the prior written consent of Red Bear or John Madden. All rights reserved.<br>Officially Licensed Product of NFL PLAYERS INC. and NFLPLAYERS.COM';
